Package org.game.connect4.model

package org.game.connect4.model
The package includes all the models used in the Connect Four API.
  • Related Packages
    Package
    Description
    org.game.connect4
    The package serves as the starting point of the Connect Four API.
    org.game.connect4.exception
    The package includes all the custom exceptions of the Connect Four API.
    org.game.connect4.util
    The package stores all the utility classes of the Connect Four API.
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    ConnectFourStatus
    ConnectFourStatus indicates the status of the game after every move.
    GameGrid
    GameGrid represents the main grid of the ConnectFour game with slots for a token.

    GridPosition indicates the position of a token in the Connect Four game grid.
